{"tid":1670562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋又當手足係condom？幾時搞宗教自由集會啊！","createTime":"2019-10-23T04:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T05:11:53.000Z","uid":265168,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"081e8ef609f4a071a1123beeec6a885bb79758cd","tid":1670562,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"<strong>和諧唔係一百個人講同一說話<br />\n和諧係一百個人有一百句唔同說話之餘<br />\n又互相尊重<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n今日香港警方瘋狂踐踏伊斯蘭教嘅底線 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">係完全零尊重</span></strong><br />\n然後伊斯蘭教係以和平為主 警方道咗歉<br />\n清真寺嘅代表話體諒/對今次呢件事冇意見 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">係出於宗教信仰嘅尊重</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而我哋都要表明支持嘅立場！<br />\n就算清真寺代表跪低<br />\n既然改變唔到we connect嘅事實！<br />\n呢個時候我哋更加應該表明立場尊重清真寺代表嘅決定<br />\n絕不割蓆！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">係出於對宗教自由嘅尊重</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n可見香港人同班狗嘅人畜之別<br />\n<br />\n再者今次佢哋已經柒到冇朋友<br />\n如果我哋申請宗教自由嘅遊行<br />\n佢哋唔批<br />\n又係比彈藥我哋<br />\n正式煲大佢打壓宗教自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更何況其實由六月起<br />\n警方已經多次對不同宗教唔尊重<br />\n同埋打壓宗教自由<br />\n我哋唔係應該聲援下佢哋咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又話大家係手足？又話大家唔係condom？<br />\n咁幾時肯推行動po啊？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">其實我已經開咗第3個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過推到爛都推唔到上熱門<br />\n求跪大家推爆佢 唔好錯過最好時機！</span>"},{"pid":"af54f7fe5fe9c7199a0aa2928bb0329e95b7444c","tid":1670562,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:33:44.000Z","msg":"求搞手"},{"pid":"ac5f5459b776d3fa35b83d32d10b0eb2a25643a4","tid":1670562,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:33:54.000Z","msg":"週末好定係平日好？"},{"pid":"1d455cc6040428d98742e485cdf4a4f770384da0","tid":1670562,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"[可唔可以大和解］加泰搞手 全香港人求下你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669934</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"138f99776ab93088f900b935930cde3b40d48d1e","tid":1670562,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"集會好定遊行好？"},{"pid":"4bfde5201564355beaef6daef1c2bf4a47cac8e7","tid":1670562,"uid":265168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"大家記得宗教嘅post唔好用豬仔同狗仔icon 以示尊重啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d365d89e19eb2dc3f7b58eb33b1dd1b671c375","tid":1670562,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:36:43.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"0673050ad70d10e39b09435cf2ea926bb8e05ba5","tid":1670562,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:41:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55572cfffdaba26f9abe0a3b9f5db80c761659b9","tid":1670562,"uid":277912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"138f99776ab93088f900b935930cde3b40d48d1e","tid":1670562,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"集會好定遊行好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:48:00.000Z","msg":"遊行"},{"pid":"61fafae3bbc87dcee5c38acf84b2ac70c159b7d2","tid":1670562,"uid":265168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母我開埋呢次就唔撚開啦<br />\n根本p牌就係冇人權<br />\n點撚樣都唔會上到熱門"},{"pid":"2986331a9cdaf580e2d13dccccf09711c874c43b","tid":1670562,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:00:06.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"834a0db3988adec67c9989ea22b48ce7aa4c53f3","tid":1670562,"uid":41005,"l